### Family Kanban Board API Tests
### Use with REST Client extension for VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get Full Board
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/board

### Update Board Settings
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/board
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Family HQ",
    "theme": "light"
}

### Get All Columns
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/columns

### Create a New Column
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/columns
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Waiting",
    "orderIndex": 4
}

### Update a Column
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/columns/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Backlog",
    "orderIndex": 0
}

### Delete a Column
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/columns/5

### Get All Cards
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cards

### Create a New Card
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cards
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "columnId": 1,
    "title": "Buy groceries",
    "description": "Milk, eggs, bread",
    "color": "#81b29a",
