### Delete a Card
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/cards/1

### Reorder Cards (Move card between columns)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cards/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "orders": [
        {"id": 1, "columnId": 2, "orderIndex": 0},
        {"id": 2, "columnId": 2, "orderIndex": 1}
    ]
}

